This is my second release. I hope you enjoy it! Very much a beta.. But its totally playable as it is. My clan enjoys it thoroughly!

I want to add ambient sound and perhaps some wind to the final.

Known Issues:
Nav file not included as bots tend to.. get confused.. I will, however, create a full nav mesh
for the final release.
Some textures seem stretched, they are. I will fix all that if I know people are using it.
